{"tid":273714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一國兩制 呃足廿年 中共領導 滾出香港","createTime":"2017-06-06T19:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T02:05:17.000Z","uid":35699,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3eba898c87598ea2b0169c81551cc422d8a50ca1","tid":273714,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T19:16:05.000Z","msg":"今年七月一日是香港回歸20周年兼林鄭月娥新班子上任的日子，加上國家主席習近平預料訪港，令該日子政治色彩特濃。民間人權陣線一如往年會舉辦遊行，據聞今年原本的大會主題口號為「一國兩制 呃足廿年，中共領導 滾出香港」，但由於尺度過激，內部有多達五分一成員團體反對，認為鼓吹仇恨和港獨等，民陣最終急忙修訂字眼降溫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人想印番原有口號一齊玩?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfdc771f4bc692fa48bfd79729205b420c483c2","tid":273714,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T20:32:36.000Z","msg":"鳩行鳩叫都驚過激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民姦維穩陣線"},{"pid":"f1a3dcd7f122a905c684343c784907f1c06b1583","tid":273714,"uid":61506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T20:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩行鳩叫都驚過激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民姦維穩陣線</blockquote><br />\n得五分一人反對姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民陣黎講算係進步"},{"pid":"8f2d6784c2ab468b7248d684056d62cd0a93647f","tid":273714,"uid":2603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T22:42:28.000Z","msg":"果日先有個大陸客拎住呢個環保袋 過黎問我呢壇嘢 跟住仲拎住呢個袋過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518c5381216e63e748ca34c1d165da5ef7358f38","tid":273714,"uid":2603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T22:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果日先有個大陸客拎住呢個環保袋 過黎問我呢壇嘢 跟住仲拎住呢個袋過關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><b